raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"photography_club_house\")
Mabel: Hey babe, where are you?
Player: I'm at home? Why?
Mabel: I think I'm gonna go home now
Player: Wait you're still there? 😅
Mabel: Mhmm
Mabel: I decided to take a short nap after I helped pack up
Mabel: I was so tired 🫠
Player: Does your head still hurt?
Mabel: No not anymore!!
Mabel: It's better now
Player: Good! Did you have a good time?
Mabel: Uhm... Yeah mostly!
Mabel: Thought: Apart from the kiss business that nearly killed me
Player: Get some sleep at home then
Mabel: I knowww, classes are tomorrow 😱
Mabel: It's like super past my bedtime too ugh
Mabel: But it's so dark outside 😭
Player: Oh no 😕
if Story.has_flag(\"JasonRt\"):
	=> JasonLeft
if Story.has_flag(\"CalebRt\"):
	=> CalebLeft
=> END

~ JasonLeft
Mabel: Your friend is here too 😅
Player: Oh still?
Player: What's he up to?
Mabel: Not much, just doodling on his phone like I am
Mabel: img: mabel/175
Mabel: Thought: My butt has been totally facing him this whole time but it's too awkward to change positions
Mabel: Thought: I could swear he peeks at me now and then
Player: Why do you look so nervous? 😆
Mabel: Do I???
Mabel: You're just imagining things!
Mabel: I'm totally not nervous
Mabel: Thought: Was it babe's friend I kissed?
Mabel: Thought: What was his name again?
Mabel: Thought: I could swear he smells exactly the same
Mabel: Maybe I'm dizzy from fainting still, don't worry hehe 😵‍💫
Player: That sounds worrying just a little
Mabel: Alright, I'll get ready to leave
Mabel: But it's SUPER dark outside ☹️
Mabel: How am I supposed to get home?
Player: With your legs
Mabel: Baaaabe 😗 Seriously
Player: Do you want me to call Jason to drop you off home? 😁
Mabel: That's so embarrassing omg
Player: Is Caleb not there then?
Mabel: He's busy cleaning up some spilled drinks 😭
Player: Well how else are you gonna get home??
Mabel: Fiinee, he can take me I guess 🙈
Mabel: The party princess is in need of a royal escort hehe 😊
Player: Idk if Jason is much of a royal escort 😂
Player: But I'll call him now
Mabel: Thanks baaabe! 😚
do advance_time(0, 10)
do Story.set_location(\"town\")
Player: On your way?
Mabel: Mhmm!
Mabel: img: mabel/178
Mabel: Hello 😊
