Mabel: I think he's still really drunk lol
Player: Should I tell him off? 🤣
Mabel: No no silly, I think it's fine
Mabel: Thought: It's distracting me from how scary it is
Mabel: PinkThought: He is a little close though, eep
=> Mid

~ CalebLeft
Mabel: Caleb is just sitting here on the couch with me too
Player: Oh still?
Player: What's he up to?
Mabel: Not much, just doodling on his phone like I am
Mabel: Thought: My butt has been totally facing him this whole time but it's too awkward to change positions
Mabel: img: mabel/175
Player: Why do you look so nervous? 😆
Mabel: Do I???
Mabel: You're just imagining things!
Mabel: I'm totally not nervous
Mabel: Thought: Was it Caleb?
Mabel: Thought: Who did I kiss??
