Mabel: Alright I'll get ready to leave
Mabel: But it's super dark outside ☹️
Mabel: How am I supposed to get home?
Player: With your legs
Mabel: Baaaabe 😗 Seriously
Player: Ask Caleb to walk you home maybe?
Mabel: I..
Mabel: Huh?? Are you serious?
Player: How else are you going to get home?
Mabel: Uhm.. I don't know 😅
Player: There you go
Player: Want me to text him?
Mabel: NO!!
Mabel: I meaaaan, I'll ask him myself 😛
Mabel: Thought: Gee I can do some things by myself y'know
Mabel: Okay brb
do advance_time(0, 10)
do Story.set_location(\"town\")
Player: On your way?
Mabel: Mhmm!
Mabel: Sorry, we were just chatting
Mabel: img: mabel/176
Mabel: Hello 😊
Player: Hii
Mabel: Caleb knows everything about everything!
=> Mid

~ Mid
Mabel: Oh!! You know what's interesting?
Mabel: Thought: Huh?
Mabel: Thought: Oh that's the girl that lives across from me
Mabel: Thought: Did she just... WINK AT ME?
do heart(1)
Mabel: Thought: NO NO NO
Player: Hello?
Mabel: PinkThought: HE ISN'T MY BOYFRIEND!!
Player: Earth to babe
Mabel: Gah, I'm HERE!!
Mabel: Sorry just distracted
Mabel: Babe do you know who kissed me!?
Player: What's with that all of a sudden 😅
Mabel: I'm just so curious omg
Mabel: It's so weird not knowing 😣
Mabel: Like what if I never find out 😱
Mabel: I don't think I could live with that my WHOLE LIFE
Player: Well why don't you figure it out detective Mabel
Mabel: Hmph, you won't just tell me?
Mabel: Besides, I'm a spy not a detective 🙄
