Player: Oh no 😂
Mabel: 🥺🥺🥺
Mabel: Pwetty pweaaase
Player: Fine 😆
Player: He's right there with you
Mabel: Thought: I KNEW ITTT
Mabel: PinkThought: Why am I celebrating this actually??
do heart(1)
Mabel: Oh uhm... really?
Mabel: Really really??
