~ CalebLeft2
Mabel: PinkThought: Me and Caleb really kissed?
Player: Why? You don't believe me? 😁
Mabel: PinkThought: But he's Naomi's boyfriend..
Mabel: PinkThought: Is that really okay??
if Story.has_flag(\"Naomi1\"):
