- Not at all
	Player: Not at all
	Mabel: Okay well that makes me feel 2% less guilty 🙃
- I want you to do what you feel like doing
	Player: I want you to do what you feel like doing
	Mabel: I don't even know what I feel like doing 😭
Mabel: PinkThought: But.. I want to have the fun everyone around me is having
Mabel: PinkThought: It's just a small kiss right?
do heart(2)
Mabel: PinkThought: Babe doesn't mind and it's not hurting anyone.. right?
Mabel: How do I uhm.. y'know... ask?
Mabel: I've never asked and my head is spinning a little
- Just ask!
	Player: Just ask!
	Mabel: Really? What if he says no?? 😳
	Mabel: Isn't that like super awkward?
	Player: He would have said no the first time in the dark room
	Mabel: T-true..
- Make it really obvious
	Player: Make it really obvious
	Mabel: What's that supposed to mean? 😅
	Player: Just go up to him and pucker up 😚
	Mabel: Babe you are NOT funny right now 😭
	Player: It came out funny but I mean it 😆
	Player: Hey you did it to me at the party, just do it again
