Mabel: But I'm gonna go home and straight to sleep after this
Mabel: I'll be too embarrassed to talk about it
Player: Haha sure thing
Mabel: Talk to you tomorrow babe 😳
Player: Bye, gn 😊
Player: And have fun 😉
Mabel: Love you 🙈
